{"tid":824516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最期待的畫面】三星 Note 9 爆咗啦～","createTime":"2018-09-17T06:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T13:29:09.000Z","uid":27240,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b14442cfcd06146d32d494536b664cba8e6cb4e","tid":824516,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"對於 Galaxy Note 7 的全球連環爆炸事件，引起全球航空禁攜機上飛機，最後全球回收，成為全球「最短命手機」，估計大家可能仍然心有餘悸。今年來到 Note 9，不幸的事又再發生，全球首宗 Note 9 意外在開賣後不足一個月就已經發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/140326_676819a9efd8d641ac6cb6ca824e208a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F140326_676819a9efd8d641ac6cb6ca824e208a.jpg&h=afbf2b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在紐約的 Diane Chung 當時正在皇后區 Bayside 公寓乘搭升降機，她發現手機有點熱，於是停止使用並放入手袋，之後手機開始發出刺耳的聲音並開始釋出濃煙。於是她快速拿出手機，並放到地上。Diane Chung表示當時極度恐慌，升降機內只有其一人，她立即按下升降機按鈕令，門打開後正好在公寓大堂，於是她快速把地上的手機踢出門口，一名路人幫忙用水澆熄手機。<br />\n<br />\n事件之後 Diane Chung 通過律師向 Samsung 提出訴訟，她認為 Samsung 應知 Note 9 有缺憾，要求 Samsung 賠償損失及提出銷售禁令。Samsung 回應「未收到涉及 Galaxy Note9 的類似事件的任何報告，我們正在調查此事。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Samsung 爆炸小檔案：</span></strong><br />\n在 Galaxy Note 7 爆炸事件發生初期，Samsung 一直對外否認自身產品設計有問題，甚至有地區服務點認為是用戶自家使用不當引致，最後爆炸事件完全不能停止。Samsung 在輿論壓力下終全球回收。半年之後，Samsung 發表調查報告，終承認自身電池設計在製造過程中產生問題。全球回收超過250萬部。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 7 當時使用 3500mAh電池，而到了 Galaxy Note 8 Samsung 改用低一點的 3300mAh 電池，不過 Galaxy Note 9 卻是全系列最大電池 4000mAh。估計如果爆起來威力亦是歷來最強。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2Fgalaxy-note-9-explosion%2F&d=2HgjR%2BtmD%2FzjEt0aPko%2FQfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=1d9a9723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e50c8481d6f2b2a0105360a71f6c0a075a346a1","tid":824516,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"打手全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b65384337f503a5244dfdd85f7c71bff73576b9","tid":824516,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e50c8481d6f2b2a0105360a71f6c0a075a346a1","tid":824516,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"打手全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"iPhone 唔會爆嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母屌你老母屌你老母屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d029b54a5fbe73ac14a2816319bdd1c91090e79","tid":824516,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e50c8481d6f2b2a0105360a71f6c0a075a346a1","tid":824516,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"打手全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"等睇三星狗入黎屌 iPhone 都有爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf2edd762491d2e5d2fa397e80dd50d3ccc94bc","tid":824516,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d029b54a5fbe73ac14a2816319bdd1c91090e79","tid":824516,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e50c8481d6f2b2a0105360a71f6c0a075a346a1","tid":824516,"uid":